                            </p>
                            <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-lg mt-1">Buy Now</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-8 col-lg-4">
                    <div class="card border-primary border-2">
                        <div class="card-header text-center text-primary">Most Popular</div>
                        <div class="card-body text-center py-2">
                            <h4 class="card-title">Complete Edition</h4>
                            <p class="card-subtitle">eBook download & updates</p>
                            <p class="display-5 my-2 text-primary fw-bold">$18.99</p>
                            <p class="card-text mx-3 text-muted d-none d-lg-block">
                                Suitable for anyone looking for a deeper understanding of 
                                nutrition and how to use natural remedies for healings
                                and optimal health.
                            </p>
                            <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-lg mt-0">Buy Now</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-8 col-lg-4">
                    <div class="card border-1">
                        <div class="card-header text-center text-primary">Advanced</div>
                        <div class="card-body text-center py-2">
                            <h4 class="card-title">Ultimate Edition</h4>
                            <p class="card-subtitle">download, updates & extras</p>
                            <p class="display-5 my-2 text-primary fw-light">$24.99</p>
                            <p class="card-text mx-3 text-muted d-none d-lg-block">
                                Suitable for anyone who already has healthcare background
                                or is pursuing a career in medicine, clinical nutrition, or
                                registered dietitian.
                            </p>
                            <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-lg mt-1">Buy Now</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div> <!-- end of row -->

        </div> <!-- end of container-lg -->

    </section>
    

    <!-- topics at a glance -->
    <!-- using accordions which are new to bootstrap 5 -->
    <section id="topics">
        <div class="container-md">
 
            <div class="text-center">
                <h2 class="text-center">
                    <i class="bi bi-book-half"></i>
                    Inside the Book
                </h2>
                <p class="lead text-muted">A Quick Glance at the Topics you'll Learn</p>
            </div>

            <!-- ROW: -->
            <div class="row my-0 justify-content-around align-items-center g-5">

                <!-- IMAGE -->
                <div class="col-6 col-lg-4">
                    <img class="img-fluid" src="/images/kindle_reader.jpg" alt="kindle reader">
                </div>

                <!-- ACCORDION -->
                <!-- for smaller screen the accordion will be shown at 100% of width until 
                     it reaches the large screen, then it will be shown with 6 col width -->

                <div class="col-lg-7">
 
                    <div class="accordion" id="chapters">

                        <!-- ITEM: -->
                        <div class="accordion-item">
        
                            <!-- ITEM HEADER: -->
                            <!-- aria-expanded="true" as the first item is open initially -->
                            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="heading-1">
                                
                                <button class="accordion-button" type="button"
                                        data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#chapter-1"
                                        aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="chapter-1">
                                        <span class="px-2"><i class="bi bi-lungs-fill"></i></span>
                                        Part 1 - Understanding the Elements of Health
                                </button>
                            </h2>
        
                            <!-- ITEM CONTENT: -->
                            <!-- id has to be "chapter-1" because data-bs-target="#chapter-1" -->
                            <div id="chapter-1" class="accordion-collapse collapse show"
                                 aria-labelledby="heading-1" data-bs-parent="#chapters">
                                <div class="accordion-body">
                                    <p>
                                        Individual nutrients differ in form and function, 
                                        and in the amount needed by the body; however, 
                                        they are all vital to our health. 
                                    </p>
                                    <p>
                                        Research has shown that each part of the body 
                                        contains high concentrations of certain nutrients. 
                                        A deficiency of those nutrients will cause the body part 
                                        to malfunction and eventually break down. To keep this 
                                        from happening, we need a proper diet and appropriate 
                                        nutritional supplements.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
        
                            <!-- ITEM HEADER: -->
                            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="heading-2">
                                <button class="accordion-button" type="button"
                                        data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#chapter-2"
                                        aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="chapter-2">
                                        <span class="px-2"><i class="bi bi-capsule"></i></span>
                                        Part 2 - The Disorders
                                </button>
                            </h2>
        
                            <!-- ITEM CONTENT: -->
                            <!-- id has to be "chapter-2" because data-bs-target="#chapter-2" -->
                            <div id="chapter-2" class="accordion-collapse collapse collapse"
                                 aria-labelledby="heading-2" data-bs-parent="#chapters">
                                <div class="accordion-body">
                                    <p>
                                        Part 1 explored the nutritional and dietary needs of the body. 
                                        In order to be well, the parts of the body must be fueled properly 
                                        so that breakdown does not occur.
                                    </p>
                                    <p>
                                       Your health care provider may recommend that certain diagnostic tests 
                                       be performed to help in making a diagnosis. Once a diagnosis has been 
                                       confirmed, refer to the appropriate dietary guidelines, recommendations, 
                                       and supplementation program to help speed your recovery.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
        
                            
                            <!-- ITEM HEADER: -->
                            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="heading-3">
                                <button class="accordion-button" type="button"
                                        data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#chapter-3"
                                        aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="chapter-3">
                                        <span class="px-2"><i class="bi bi-egg-fried"></i></span>
                                        Part 3 - Remedies and Therapies
                                </button>
                            </h2>
        
                            <!-- ITEM CONTENT: -->
                            <!-- id has to be "chapter-3" because data-bs-target="#chapter-3" -->
                            <div id="chapter-3" class="accordion-collapse collapse collapse"
                                 aria-labelledby="heading-3" data-bs-parent="#chapters">
                                <div class="accordion-body">
                                    <p>
                                        In Part 2, various treatment programs were recommended for 
                                        each of the health problems discussed. Part 3 explains how 
                                        to implement some of the remedies and therapies discussed earlier, 
                                        as well as providing information about some cutting-edge technologies 
                                        that are showing promise in the treatment of various disorders.
                                    </p>
                                    <p>
                                        After learning about what is available out there, you will be able to 
                                        choose the options that are most suitable for you and your situation.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            
                        </div> <!-- accordion-item -->
                    </div> <!-- end of accordion -->
                </div> <!-- outer div of accordion -->
            </div> <!-- row -->
        </div> <!-- container-md -->
    </section>


    <!-- reviews list -->
    <section id="reviews" class="">

        <!-- CONTAINER: -->
        <!-- need a container inside section -->
        <div class="container-lg">

            <!-- PART 1: HEADING -->
            <div class="text-center">
                <h2><i class="bi bi-stars text-dark"></i>Book Reviews</h2>
                <p class="lead">What Readers have said About the Book</p>
            </div>

            <!-- PART 2: ROW -->
            <div class="row justify-content-center my-0">

                <!-- COL -->
                <div class="col-lg-8">

                    <!-- LIST GROUP -->
                    <div class="list-group">

                        <!-- LIST GROUP ITEM -->
                        <div class="list-group-item py-2">
                            <div class="pb-2"> <!-- padding at bottom -->
                                <i class="bi bi-star-fill text-dark"></i>
                                <i class="bi bi-star-fill text-dark"></i>
                                <i class="bi bi-star-fill text-dark"></i>
